492
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:46,100
So we are all part and parcel of One Being.

493
00:38:46,367 --> 00:38:57,567
As you call them, the microcosm and the macrocosm.

494
00:38:59,234 --> 00:39:02,567
And only thing [is] the ones which are awakened

495
00:39:02,773 --> 00:39:05,133
will help to awaken the rest of it.

496
00:39:05,267 --> 00:39:08,979
That doesn’t mean anybody is superior or higher or lower.

497
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,500
There is no obligation.

498
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:14,133
Like my own finger paining if I try to rub it,

499
00:39:14,234 --> 00:39:22,267
am I obliging that finger? No, I am not. Because I can’t live without that.

500
00:39:22,612 --> 00:39:27,351
