some of the Sahaja Yogis will come and see what the situation is,

504
00:39:39,694 --> 00:39:44,334
what are the centres in trouble. Nobody should feel bad about it.

505
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:48,621
With all respect to you it will be done.

506
00:39:48,812 --> 00:39:53,367
So one should not feel bad or sad about it [or] in anyway hurt.

507
00:39:53,467 --> 00:40:02,367
Why I am saying so [is] because, you see sometimes people feel

508
00:40:02,426 --> 00:40:08,159
